detaileddescription.para:
We should set Geometry and Shader before attach to actor. If not, exception throwed.
@SINCE_2_4.9
A handle to the Renderer

@SINCE_1_1.43 

handle



Handle to an object

@SINCE_1_9.22 

rhs



A reference to the moved handle

@SINCE_1_1.43 

geometry



The geometry to be used by this renderer

@SINCE_1_1.43 

